\CE[94]\CE[95]\N<Jazz>Do you know a town called Hakudeti, it's located to the
southwest from here?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Ah yes, it's a fairly large town, isn't it?
And that area is also popular because
there are very few monsters around.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>Yes, that one. \.There has been a disturbance
in Hakudeti and the surrounding area.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>As you said, I thought that area was a peaceful
land without any demon incursions due to its location.
However, it seems the number of monsters has increased over the past year.

\N<Jazz>Furthermore, it seems that a new dungeon has recently been
discovered nearby.
\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>A dungeon in a place like that...

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>Ah, it seems that the sisters of the Hakudeti Holy
Demon Church discovered it. \.It looks like it's
not that big, but there are magical beasts that
even the guards can't handle, and they say there
aren't enough people to deal with security in the
surrounding area.

\N<Jazz>And according to the priest of the Holy Demon
Church, I've heard that there are also
abnormalities within the town itself.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>It seems to be only a general feeling, but I've been
told that the number of criminals and potential
criminals in the town has increased. Compared to
 a year ago, there has also been an increase in
unsavory individuals, and the overall atmosphere
of the town has become heavier.

\N<Jazz>It seems to be quite significant, and to put it
simply, security has deteriorated. The
increase in monsters and the discovery of dungeons
have led to an increase in rough bounty hunters
and adventurers as well, which seems to be one of the main
causes.

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I see... and if the priest feels that way, it
doesn't seem like it's just a gut feeling.

\CE[79]\N<Jazz>Right. If it were as simple as reducing the number of
monsters and sealing the dungeon, then the problem
would be easy to solve...

\N<Jazz>This is just a hunch, but \....\....\....\...., I
have a bad feeling about this. It feels like
there's some sort of scheme behind this. That's
why this mission can only be entrusted to someone
with a certain level of skill.

\N<Jazz>So Rain, it was decided that you would be the one. The
other holy knights are all away on business
dealing with the recent movements of the demon
army, so it will be a solo mission. But they all
agreed that you should be fine... and I also felt

\CE[94]\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────Despite saying that you share the same feeling,

\CE[79]\CE[94]\CE[95]\N<Jazz>No, I acknowledge that you are suitable for the

\N<Jazz>─────And... seeing as I won't able to meet with
